{"tid":111460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母, 長毛真係出黎選特首呀,飯民比撚晒提名票佢啦","createTime":"2017-02-07T12:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T01:41:54.000Z","uid":28934,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"79d27c511b52702d8099dc872ee2c6f53faaf528","tid":111460,"uid":28934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:11:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁就比長毛同淋病入閘, 最後各位港豬捱淋病10年, 日日我要真普選, 反對23條立法, 平反831, 年年64維園再見,諗起都想射精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/15747536_801446433327637_6674320632793071519_n_a3Vi8_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F15747536_801446433327637_6674320632793071519_n_a3Vi8_1200x0.jpg&h=d3d84e16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ziines.com/ziines-user-upload/upload/2016/03/10/1687_20160310161600_56e12d40c3081.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ziines.com%2Fziines-user-upload%2Fupload%2F2016%2F03%2F10%2F1687_20160310161600_56e12d40c3081.gif&h=9a40cb33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梁國雄明宣布出選特首　力爭公民提名　陳志全、朱凱&amp;#24312;、羅冠聰撐場<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/梁國雄明宣布出選特首-力爭公民提名-陳志全-朱凱&amp;#24312;-羅冠聰撐場/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%84%E6%98%8E%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%87%BA%E9%81%B8%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96-%E5%8A%9B%E7%88%AD%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D-%E9%99%B3%E5%BF%97%E5%85%A8-%E6%9C%B1%E5%87%B1%26%2324312%3B-%E7%BE%85%E5%86%A0%E8%81%B0%E6%92%90%E5%A0%B4%2F&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a00ebf1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%84%E6%98%8E%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%87%BA%E9%81%B8%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96-%E5%8A%9B%E7%88%AD%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D-%E9%99%B3%E5%BF%97%E5%85%A8-%E6%9C%B1%E5%87%B1%26%2324312%3B-%E7%BE%85%E5%86%A0%E8%81%B0%E6%92%90%E5%A0%B4%2F&h=978155ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/梁國雄明宣布出選特首-力爭公民提名-陳志全-朱凱&amp;#24312;-羅冠聰撐場/</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n社民連議員梁國雄將於明早舉行記者會，宣布出選特首，並會全力爭取公民提名。除了梁國雄外，人民力量陳志全、朱凱&amp;#24312;及香港眾志羅冠聰，也會出席記者會。<br />\n<br />\n社民連、人民力量、朱凱&amp;#24312;團隊、香港眾志等傍晚發出採訪通知，指梁國雄將於明早10時半宣布「2017特首民投」民間提名，以及參選行政長官選舉之決定。<br />\n<br />\n採訪通知指出「人大831」之下重啟政改、23條勢捲土重來、「人大釋法」取消議員資格、「官商鄉黑」勾結無日休止、全民退保等民生政策遙遙無期，「民主派沒有逃避嚴峻現實的理由，只有負起重申民主原則、民生綱領的責任。」<br />\n<br />\n由佔中發起人戴耀廷及多個民間團體發起「2017特首民投」，今日開放予市民就提名參選人表態，暫列出12個公開表態參選及已報名參與的「民間參選人」供市民選擇，暫時以曾俊華領先。<br />\n<br />\n截至晚上7時20分，曾俊華獲2586人提名，胡國興獲858人提名、梁國雄獲754人提名，排行第三。部分民主派選委表示，有意參考「2017特首民投」的結果提名。<br />\n<br />\n根據計劃，「民間參選人」如取得全港300多萬合資格選民1%、即37790人提名後，即可成為「民間特首候選人」，連同獲150名提委入閘的特首參選人，參與下一階段3月10至19日舉行的民間特首投票。"},{"pid":"e73e1e0f6bae1a37f749923b9b087066f36a2099","tid":111460,"uid":22479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:17:36.000Z","msg":"真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：🎗"},{"pid":"1eba54022d8afe1109e655014b4b5598c9f4205b","tid":111460,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:39:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e301b041b2687e5e5703e69831e5c28a27c5e8a8","tid":111460,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:41:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"65513e2eea87785da215677a510f516127f607ad","tid":111460,"uid":28934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:44:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持長毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係支持淋病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s